Sensitive Personal Information
California residents have the right to limit the use of “sensitive personal information” (as defined in the CCPA) to certain purposes specified in the CCPA.  However, Mint Mobile already only collects or processes sensitive personal information with your consent and for those purposes specified in the CCPA.  Mint Mobile also does not use sensitive personal information for inferring characteristics about you.
